rule1
on dht11 do DisplayText [l1c1]House endon
on tele-dht11#Temperature do DisplayText [l1c10]%value%~dfC~20~20 endon
on tele-dht11#Humidity do Backlog var1 %value%; CalcRes 0; ADD1 0; DisplayText  [l1c18]%var1%% endon
on dht11 do DisplayText [l2c1]Street endon
on dht11 do DisplayText [l3c1]Pressure endon
on mqtt#connected DO Subscribe LetnicaT, tele/LetnicaHT/SENSOR, BMP180.Temperature ENDON
on Event#LetnicaT do DisplayText [l2c10]%value%~dfC~20~20 endon
on mqtt#connected DO Subscribe LetnicaP, tele/LetnicaHT/SENSOR, BMP180.Pressure ENDON
on Event#LetnicaP do Backlog var2 %value%; CalcRes 0; ADD2 0; DisplayText[l3c14]%var2%mmHg endon
on mqtt#connected DO Subscribe LetnicaH, tele/LetnicaHT/SENSOR, dht11.Humidity ENDON
on Event#LetnicaH do Backlog var3 %value%; CalcRes 0; ADD3 0; DisplayText[l2c18]%var3%% endon
on dht11 do DisplayText [l4c1] [T] endon
on dht11 do DisplayText [l4c16] [t] endon
on Time#Minute|1440 do DisplayText [z] endon
